{"tid":1605041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[戰術]前線或者有新戰術！泡泡魔法！","createTime":"2019-09-30T07:10:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T01:45:35.000Z","uid":180661,"like":133,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"162f2abffef2e1b14125f4cb202dccf17db89615","tid":1605041,"uid":180661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:10:12.000Z","msg":"重開！整理咗之前個po各巴打意見<br />\n大象牙膏<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kj85Wab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKj85Wab.png&h=db08c416&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XpSqWad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXpSqWad.png&h=b6bdb6b1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vnzs9vf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVnzs9vf.png&h=ab990df5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qKVv7gW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqKVv7gW.png&h=2d182852&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特點:<br />\n-物料容易準備<br />\n-發得好快 可以殺對方一個措手不及<br />\n-泡泡有顏色 可以遮擋對方視線<br />\n-啲泡泡有化學反應會發熱<br />\n-視覺效果好睇有文宣效果<br />\n <br />\n雙氧水+洗潔精+碘化鉀=🌋<br />\n擺定一桶係中間，退個陣一嘢倒落去<br />\n如果控制得好應該係唔錯嘅戰術<br />\n<br />\n化學野唔多熟<br />\n有咩唔啱<br />\n屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求下大家一齊推上熱門一齊討論！！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ergj7kxhw8k?t=353\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FErgj7kxhw8k%3Ft%3D353&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZssFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=e4b74b77\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Ergj7kxhw8k?t=353</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3P615d6aaik\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3P615d6aaik&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZssFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=f31ef958\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3P615d6aaik</a>"},{"pid":"16807f07358d9171f42a8ddef5b5764900f5ea82","tid":1605041,"uid":180661,"like