ke":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:18:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11305fd16fdc8245b2d436b0d9aceb6a3811190c","tid":1605041,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:23:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港人治港 剷除共黨</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">正名!</span></span><br />\n狗 --&gt; 港共走狗/共狗打手/金腰帶<br />\n示威者 --&gt; 香港人<br />\n死--&gt;被自殺<br />\n藍絲--&gt;港共流氓<br />\n<br />\n光頭警長劉Sir前往内地安家，民眾甚感期待<br />\n光頭<span style=\"color: red;\">走狗</span>劉Sir前往内地安家，民眾甚感期待<br />\n<br />\n[底已起] 又有隻奶共狗話示威者係曱甴<br />\n[底已起] 又有隻奶共狗話<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人</span>係曱甴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對準政權! 撐政府一律捆綁式形容!</span></span>"},{"pid":"cef80aab34df28ac73866541654be325c4cbcc1d","tid":1605041,"uid":233009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:25:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a0c5f4171bf86c58ac66b381cd466a4229bc31d9","tid":1605041,"uid":166659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:26:00.000Z","msg":"推啊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8a042dea39954752f86a1cdf9011c8ca162689f","tid":1605041,"uid":112784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:27:55.000Z","msg":"條街好大喎<br />\n<br />\n個份量要多到痴線"},{"pid":"d15932ac5b991eb87813e4216fd47c8e4d3b5454","tid":1605041,"uid":63124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f89936b34574c1ddda781c11bffeaa2edb45364","tid":1605041,"uid":9116,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:29:10.000Z","msg":"防禦戰術係咪應該升華啲好呢? 之前路障作用真係唔大，而且整既時間遠低於阻狗既時間<br />\n同埋好似琴日政總咁，啲狗由緊急門衝出咁就拉咗幾十個手足，所以一定要諗更好既防禦設施<br />\n<br />\n之前啲狗既弱點係沙田一役就盡露哂，就係怕高空擲物同地跣，<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QNu8PqYTU7U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQNu8PqYTU7U&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZssFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=ffb78289\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QNu8PqYTU7U</a><br />\n地勢呢樣冇得講，所以令喺條街都要跣鳩到班狗，之前直接淋落地，實質作用係冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3144527/org/24d3ab06899947463cffa65c73217f8e.jpg/v-ChUAw1mQqJzqjlTJKKMnXxcHPqPZ1SHZGnfx2Rp38\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3144527%2Forg%2F24d3ab06899947463cffa65c73217f8e.jpg%2Fv-ChUAw1mQqJzqjlTJKKMnXxcHPqPZ1SHZGnfx2Rp38&h=2c6682d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n建議用一定長度同闊度既帆布/跣水布甚至包書膠，放置狗有可能衝出嚟既方向，上面加洗潔精加水加花生油、一嚟唔會咁易蒸發流走，<br />\n<br />\n二嚟撤退時可以有手足扣住布既一面喺背囊拖住走，狗跟住你後面就會跣低，如果有狗捉住條布，一扯就可以隨時甩開既，<br />\n<br />\n如果有10個以上手足敢於斷後，扣住既布應該可以3線馬路都足夠COVER，但一定要有一定長度，小心因為布唔夠長反被捉住<br />\n理想效果 : <span style=\"color: red;\">(布既長度起碼要有10米以上，闊要起碼兩米，等啲狗冇得跨過去) </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pE4oIBodE30\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpE4oIBodE30&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZssFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=6e0d2315\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pE4oIBodE30</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">甚至直接加油加酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一點著就係一條防線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:31:33.000Z","msg":"唔使用帆布<br />\n最好一定係紙皮<br />\n濕到透一踩就爛個種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0ded8e9f5e8872732e3a398e4d21e180e5d236e","tid":1605041,"uid":19255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:32:36.000Z","msg":"好用喔哩個"},{"pid":"ea9505022ad3